# Optional: explicit WebSocket endpoint. If unset, the client uses
#   - ws://<page host>:8765  in dev (Vite on 5173, WS server on 8765)
#   - wss?://<page host>     in prod (single-origin server serves both)
# Override this when the WS server lives on a different host.
# VITE_WS_URL=wss://aipoker.example.com
